492
00:28:26,625 --> 00:28:28,343
Elijah! There you are.

493
00:28:28,625 --> 00:28:31,503
The name is Eliyahu.
- Yes, Elilulu.

494
00:28:31,665 --> 00:28:35,453
I didn't expect you to notice,
but we English are not accustomed

495
00:28:35,785 --> 00:28:38,094
to sweating here
like you natives.

496
00:28:38,305 --> 00:28:40,500
