to better care.

497
00:28:40,945 --> 00:28:44,176
George, put the bed back in place.
- Don't.

498
00:28:44,465 --> 00:28:46,933
George, you better put it back

499
00:28:47,065 --> 00:28:49,420
before I spit you and the Englishman
on an IV pole!

500
00:28:49,585 --> 00:28:50,301
Eliyahu...

501
00:28:50,425 --> 00:28:51,858
Who do you think you are?

502
00:28:52,025 --> 00:28:53,777
I am Rhoda's brother

503
00:28:53,945 --> 00:28:56,175
and I have the means
to give her better treatment.

504
00:28:57,985 --> 00:28:59,464
Oh, and another thing,

505
00:28:59,825 --> 00:29:04,216
I hope you are taking better care of the
Simpson residence we let you live in.

506
00:29:04,385 --> 00:29:05,215
When can I see it?

507
00:29:05,825 --> 00:29:09,181
I'll smash his teeth in...
- Eliyahu. - Stop it! - Eliyahu.

508
00:29:09,305 --> 00:29:10,454
Eliyahu, calm down!

509
00:29:10,585 --> 00:29:12,815
I don't have third-party insurance.

510
00:29:12,945 --> 00:29:16,415
Her whole family, those bastards,
they broke her heart! - Stop it!

511
00:29:16,545 --> 00:29:19,059
They broke her heart!
- Calm down.

512
00:29:19,185 --> 00:29:22,382
Eliyahu, not here. We'll make him
eat lead in the parking lot later.

513
00:29:22,545 --> 00:29:25,503
We are the best place
in Jerusalem, Lord.

514
00:29:25,905 --> 00:29:29,784
And to imagine that I was considering
living in this dreadful place,

515
00:29:29,945 --> 00:29:31,583
in an apartment
next to my sister.

516
00:29:31,745 --> 00:29:33,258
You will love it.

517
00:29:33,385 --> 00:29:34,500
And you will change your mind.

518
00:29:34,665 --> 00:29:38,544
And I will give you
the best room for a few weeks

519
00:29:38,665 --> 00:29:40,462
for a try. What do you say?

520
00:29:40,865 --> 00:29:42,344
